{"tid":511810,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"2017世界百大美女公布，周子瑜進三甲超越Nana","createTime":"2017-12-27T23:49:33.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-29T07:45:50.000Z","uid":41351,"like":34,"dislike":141,"uniUserReply":57,"replies":[{"pid":"3b69c62d0a1ca29d7be7ed8e61a61aab3cf3233b","tid":511810,"uid":41351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-27T23:49:33.000Z","msg":"〔記者陳立妍／綜合報導〕2017年進入尾聲，美國電影網站「TC Candler」公布今年的世界百大美女榜，去年勇奪第8名的韓團TWICE台灣成員子瑜，首度擊敗曾蟬聯2年冠軍的Nana榮登「亞洲最美」，亞軍為16歲的法國超模黛蘭布蘭多，冠軍則為19歲的美國女星莉扎索伯拉奧。 「TC Candler」從1990年舉辦「世界百大帥哥、美女」排行榜，除了從外表進行評選，並以文化背景、生活模式、公眾意見等多面向，選出「世界百大帥哥、美女」，榜單歷史至今已超過25年。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/28/074815_fdd6efd681a7cfe0b95286037509f762.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F28%2F074815_fdd6efd681a7cfe0b95286037509f762.jpeg&h=51b98f82&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n仲贏埋Nana"},{"pid":"24efdd14143ada8a5e817c1a20026e7a31b9f68e","tid":511810,"uid":57851,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-28T00:01:28.000Z","msg":"百大<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c391a51f62197f2d5cab83f20089d72d8aeba9e5","tid":511810,"uid":92376,"like":47,"dislike":4,"score":43,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2017-12-28T00:04:04.000Z","msg":"淨係知道呢啲榜一定一個香港都唔會有<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c84fd904b81a888fb29e58181a9ce6e3a4903be","tid":511810,"uid":113626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c391a51f62197f2d5cab83f20089d72d8aeba9e5","tid":511810,"uid":92376,"like":47,"dislike":4,"score":43,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2017-12-28T00:04:04.000Z","msg":"淨係知道呢啲榜一定一個香港都唔會有<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-28T00:04:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6c8a6a1144f2b3043dcfb53cc5b961610e908bf","tid":511810,"uid":59151,"like":145,"dislike":40,"score":105,"citedBy"